<data>&lt;div class=b&gt;&lt;a href="/"&gt;Home&lt;/a&gt; » &lt;a href="/tipitaka/12S1"&gt;12S1 Sagāthāvaggasaṃyuttapāḷi&lt;/a&gt; » &lt;a href="/tipitaka/12S1/1"&gt;1 Devatāsaṃyutta&lt;/a&gt; » &lt;a href="/tipitaka/12S1/1/1.4"&gt;1.4 Satullapakāyikavagga&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="i"&gt;1.4.6 Saddhāsutta&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=h&gt;Devatāsaṃyutta&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=h&gt;Satullapakāyikavagga&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=h&gt;Saddhāsutta&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_12S1_199"&gt; &lt;div class="divNumber"&gt;36.&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt;&lt;span class="pN"&gt;199&lt;/span&gt;Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. Atha kho sambahulā satullapakāyikā devatāyo abhikkantāya rattiyā abhikkantavaṇṇā kevalakappaṃ jetavanaṃ obhāsetvā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhaṃsu. Ekamantaṃ ṭhitā kho ekā devatā bhagavato santike imaṃ gāthaṃ abhāsi—  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_12S1_200"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt; &lt;table class="singleColumn"&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="pN"&gt;200&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;“Saddhā dutiyā purisassa hoti,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;No ce assaddhiyaṃ avatiṭṭhati;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Yaso ca kittī ca tatvassa hoti,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Saggañca so gacchati sarīraṃ vihāyā”ti.&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;/table&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_12S1_201"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt;&lt;span class="pN"&gt;201&lt;/span&gt;Atha kho aparā devatā bhagavato santike imā gāthāyo abhāsi—  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_12S1_202"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt; &lt;table class="singleColumn"&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="pN"&gt;202&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;“Kodhaṃ jahe vippajaheyya mānaṃ,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Saṃyojanaṃ sabbamatikkameyya;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Taṃ nāmarūpasmimasajjamānaṃ,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Akiñcanaṃ nānupatanti saṅgā”ti.&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;/table&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_12S1_203"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt; &lt;table class="singleColumn"&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="pN"&gt;203&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;“Pamādamanuyuñjanti,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;bālā dummedhino janā;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Appamādañca medhāvī,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;dhanaṃ seṭṭhaṃva rakkhati.&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;/table&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_12S1_204"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt; &lt;table class="singleColumn"&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="pN"&gt;204&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Mā pamādamanuyuñjetha,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;mā kāmarati santhavaṃ;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Appamatto hi jhāyanto,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;pappoti paramaṃ sukhan”ti.&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;/table&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="tn"&gt;&lt;div class=plcb&gt;&lt;a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="prevP()" id="prevL" name="273649" title="Go to previous page"&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;lt; 1.4.5 Ujjhānasaññisutta&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="upP()" id="upL" name="272690" title="Go to parent page"&gt;up&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="nextP()" id="nextL" name="273651" title="Go to next page"&gt;1.4.7 Samayasutta &amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</data>
